snippet: India made a strong reply to England's first-innings total of 477 after half-centuries by debutant Liam Dawson and number nine Adil Rashid underlined the tourists' batting depth in the fifth and final test on Saturday....
lead_paragraph: India made a strong reply to England's first-innings total of 477 after half-centuries by debutant Liam Dawson and number nine Adil Rashid underlined the tourists' batting depth in the fifth and final test on Saturday.

headline.main: India Off to Good Start After Dawson Impresses on Debut
headline.print_headline: India Off to Good Start After Dawson Impresses on Debut
